item.title: CVE-2008-10001|2024-08-07T12:03:37.149Z -- pro2col -- stingray%20fts
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as problematic, has been found in Pro2col Stingray FTS. The manipulation of the argument Username leads to cross site scripting. The attack may be initiated remotely. It is recommended to upgrade the affected component. NOTE: This vulnerability only affects products that are no longer supported by the maintainer
